                        maiores ut dolorum veritatis id praesentium sequi
                        reiciendis labore! Excepturi quam optio earum molestiae
                        blanditiis maiores!
                    </span>
                </div>

                <!-- Visión -->
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col gap-5 w-full md:w-1/2 bg-secondary p-10 items-center rounded-3xl min-h-[25vw]
               relative md:-translate-x-8 shadow-2xl z-20"
                    style="color: var(--bg-white);"
                >
                    <h1 class="text-3xl pl-2">Visión</h1>
                    <span>
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
                        Velit laborum facere placeat beatae. Reprehenderit
